      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 106: The banner is now reachable by Tab (`activeFocusOnTab: true` / `Accessible.focusable: true`) but it exposes itself as `Accessible.StaticText` and has no keyboard activation handler. Keyboard and screen-reader users can focus an item that visually behaves like a clickable donation link, but Enter/Space will not open the URL. Either do not make the container focusable, or expose it as a button/link and handle keyboard activation consistently with the MouseArea. Suggested fix:\n```suggestion\n    Keys.onReturnPressed: Qt.openUrlExternally(JamiTheme.donationUrl)\n    Keys.onEnterPressed: Qt.openUrlExternally(JamiTheme.donationUrl)\n    Keys.onSpacePressed: Qt.openUrlExternally(JamiTheme.donationUrl)\n\n    Accessible.role: Accessible.Button\n    Accessible.name: JamiStrings.donationText\n    Accessible.description: JamiStrings.donationText\n    Accessible.focusable: true\n```",
